OL,3,CLess than a quarter of BMA doctors at
OL,4,CManx Care recommend it as a workplace
OL,6,FA British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,7,Fsurvey suggests less than a quarter of
OL,8,Fdoctors at Manx Care say they would
OL,9,Frecommend it as a place to work.
OL,11,FThe annual 'Culture of Care Barometer
OL,12,FSurvey' seeks the views of doctors
OL,13,Fwith the BMA on the island, about the
OL,14,Fhealth service they work for, and the
OL,15,Fstandards of care it provides.
OL,17,FOver 60% of those asked whether the
OL,18,FTrust listens to staff views replied
OL,19,F'disagreed' or 'strongly disagreed'.
