OL,3,CLess than a quarter of BMA doctors at
OL,4,CManx Care recommend it as a workplace
OL,6,FThe majority of respondents added they
OL,7,Ffeel respected by their co-workers,
OL,8,Fand they are treated with respect by
OL,9,Ftheir immediate manager, but only 13%
OL,10,Fsaid they see evidence of good
OL,11,Fleadership at senior levels.
OL,13,FAdditionally, only a quarter of
OL,14,Frespondents believe they have the
OL,15,Fresources they need to do their job
OL,16,Fwell, and just over a third say they
OL,17,Fhad the time they need to do their job
OL,18,Fwell.
