OL,3,CLess than a quarter of BMA doctors at
OL,4,CManx Care recommend it as a workplace
OL,6,FDr Prakash Thiagarajan, the chair of
OL,7,Fthe Isle of Man Medical Society, said:
OL,8,F"Once again, we are seeing survey
OL,9,Fresults that tell us very little is
OL,10,Fimproving in Manx Care.
OL,12,F"Doctors without the time or the
OL,13,Fresources to care for their patients
OL,14,Fas they'd like to or do their jobs as
OL,15,Fthey should.
OL,17,F"Less than a third of those who
OL,18,Freplied feel proud to work for Manx
OL,19,FCare and less than a fifth believe
OL,20,Fthat unacceptable behaviours are dealt
OL,21,Fwith consistently.
