OL,3,CLess than a quarter of BMA doctors at
OL,4,CManx Care recommend it as a workplace
OL,6,F"People on the Isle of Man should not
OL,7,Fbe cared for by doctors who are
OL,8,Fdemoralised and we should not have a
OL,9,Fhealth service staffed by doctors who
OL,10,Fdo not believe they are valued by
OL,11,Fsenior leaders at Manx Care.
OL,13,F"We have started a dialogue with
OL,14,FTeresa Cope, the Chief Executive of
OL,15,FManx Care to ask how these issues will
OL,16,Fbe addressed as well as ones on pay
OL,17,Fand safer staffing levels."
