OL,3,CLess than a quarter of BMA doctors at
OL,4,CManx Care recommend it as a workplace
OL,6,FThis survey comes after an external
OL,7,Freport found issues with how Manx Care
OL,8,Foperates independently from the Isle
OL,9,Fof Man's government, and that the
OL,10,Fisland's health and social care model
OL,11,Fwas not working as well as originally
OL,12,Fintended following its creation in
OL,13,F2019.
OL,15,FThe BMA's Chair of Council, Dr Tom
OL,16,FDolphin is due to visit the Isle of
OL,17,FMan on Friday 6th February to meet
OL,18,Fgovernment ministers, as well as
OL,19,Fdoctors from Manx Care and listen to
OL,20,Ftheir concerns.
