OL,3,CLess than a quarter of BMA doctors at
OL,4,CManx Care recommend it as a workplace
OL,6,FIn a statement, Manx Care said it has
OL,7,F"not yet had time to fully digest the
OL,8,FBMA's Culture of Care Barometer survey
OL,9,Fdata, but initial analysis of the data
OL,10,Fsuggests colleagues are experiencing
OL,11,Fsignificant improvements across each
OL,12,Fof the survey's key themes". 27 out of
OL,13,F30 responses show year-on-year
OL,14,Fimprovement.
