OL,6,FThe organisation added that it will
OL,7,F"continue to work sympathetically and
OL,8,Fin confidence with all our colleagues
OL,9,Fincluding in partnership with BMA to
OL,10,Fdeliver our goal which is to be the
OL,11,Fbest small island health and care
OL,12,Fservice in the world."
